data.description: Now offering $5,000 in seller concessions!! This stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. An office provides a quiet, private space for remote work; while the large loft area is the perfect versatile space that can be used as a game room, second living area, home gym, or homeschooling - the possibilities are endless. The kitchen has painted cabinets and updated appliances with a breakfast nook to make your morning routines a breeze. A first level primary suite is the cherry on top for this expansive floor plan; equipped with a garden tub, dual vanities, and a large walk-in closet. The love and care that have gone into this home is accentuated by the perfectly manicured lawn and well thought out backyard. Located in Bulverde Village with award winning schools in NEISD, you do not want to miss the opportunity to make this home yours.
